## Core product concept

- **Community-first:** Gotra, aakna, kuldevi, nakshatra, manglik, mama naam are first-class fields. Gotra exclusion enforced at **DB/query level** (default ON).
- **Freemium:** Two tiers only — **Free** vs **Paid** (no multi-tier in Phase 1).
- **Trust:** Admin-moderated profiles/photos, verification badge, report/block, Samaj partnership positioning.
- **Matching IP:** 10-step weighted scoring (hard filters → manglik → location → prefs → completeness → recency → mutual fit → paid boost → Kundli → exclusions). Nightly cron pre-computes suggestions.
- **Connection flow:** Interest → email notify → accept/decline → **offline** contact (phone/WhatsApp). No in-app chat/calls in Phase 1.
- **Kundli:** Ashtakoot via `astrology-js` in backend. Badges: Uttam/उत्तम, Madhyam/मध्यम, Vichar Yogya/विचार योग्य.
- **Bilingual:** Hindi + English from day one. No hardcoded UI strings. Web: `next-intl`. Mobile: `i18next`. Locales: `packages/shared/locales/{en,hi}.json`.

## 9 screens (Phase 1)

Splash/Auth → Profile Wizard (5 steps) → Own Profile → Other Profile → Match Feed → Interests Inbox (Received/Sent/Accepted/Views) → Search → Hamburger Drawer → Settings.

Visual reference: `docs/GahoiSarthi_Screens_v1.html`. Primary palette: Sacred Gold `#B5620E`, Ivory `#FDFAF5`.

## Locked stack

| Layer | Choice |
|-------|--------|
| Monorepo | Turborepo + pnpm |
| Backend | Node + Express + TS → **Render** (ALL business logic here) |
| DB | Supabase **PostgreSQL only** — no Auth/Edge/Realtime/Storage |
| ORM | Prisma v5 |
| Web/Admin | Next.js 14 → Netlify |
| Mobile | React Native + Expo SDK 51 |
| Images | Cloudflare R2 (private bucket, signed URLs) |
| Email/OTP | Resend |
| Payments | Razorpay |

**Structure:** `apps/{backend,web,admin,mobile}` · `packages/{shared,email-templates}`

## Non-negotiable rules

- ALL business logic on Render backend — **never** Supabase Edge Functions
- Never `prisma.$queryRawUnsafe()` — parameterised queries only
- **Three-tier profile visibility:** free → no PII | paid+no match → masked | paid+matched → full
- Use `@gahoisarthi/shared/utils/masking` — never roll your own
- Contact PII never in list/search responses
- **Cursor pagination only** — never offset/skip/page params; no total in search
- JWT **RS256** explicitly — never HS256 or `none`
- R2 private; signed URLs ~2hr expiry; keys `profiles/{userId}/{uuid}.jpg`
- API envelope: `{ success, data, error, meta: { next_cursor? } }`

## Free vs Paid (summary)

| Capability | Free | Paid |
|------------|------|------|
| Daily match cards | 5 | 30 + Top Pick |
| Interests/day | 5 | Unlimited |
| Received interests visible | Latest 3 | All |
| Contact details | Never | After mutual accept |
| Advanced search / Kundli report | No | Yes |

